--------------------Components of power BI-------------------------------------
1. Powerquery
2. Powerpivot
3.powerview
4.powerBI service
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
why powerBI?
1. many features (functions, visuals)
2. trending one
3. cheapest tool
4. data connectivity from many sources (excel, word)
--------------------------how it works?--------------------------------------
1.power bi desktop- developers work on this part like cleaning data, data modelling and when the data has be shared to the client then powerBI service takes place.
2.power bi service- we share files to clients through this.
